Goa2 chhoa7 Ho-lan siong7-boe2-tin7 e5 pou7-tui7 kiann5 siann5-goa7 hit-tiau5 sio2-lou7, tit8-tit8 hiong3 Erasmus khi3, chun2-pi7 chiunn7-chun5, si3-khou-ui5 u7 Koxinga e5 peng-a2 ka7 goan2 kam3-si7, goa2 sim-cheng5 tim5-tang7, chhin-chhiunn7 sim-lai7 u7 chit8-liap8 kui-ban7-kin e5 thih-thui5, teh kah goa2 be7 chhoan2-khui3--tit, na2 kiann5 e5 si5, kam2-kak lou7 phu5-phu5, kiann5-tioh8 bo5 siann2 teng7-tauh, si3-khou-lian3-tng2 e5 mih8-kiann7, goa2 khoann3-bo5 thiann-bo5, it-tit8 kau3 chhinn-chham2 e5 khau3-siann chng3 jip8-khi3 goa2 e5 hi7-khang, chiah hiong5-hiong5 chheng-chhenn2.
